### Enhancement 4: Contingency Planning — CP-2(1), CP-4(2), CP-9(8)

**CP-2(1) Contingency Plan — Coordinate with Related Plans:** The High baseline CP-2 requires a contingency plan. This enhancement requires explicit coordination between the OpenMRS contingency plan and MyClinic's broader emergency operations plan — ensuring that clinical downtime procedures are integrated into the clinic's overall emergency response framework, not maintained as a separate IT document that clinical staff do not know exists.

